!Topic 72 Scroll Back (UpArrow)

While in scrollback mode, the following keys are active:

    Up Arrow  - up one line       Down Arrow  - down one line
    PgUp      - up one page       PgDn        - down one page
    Home      - top of scroll     End         - bottom of scroll
